<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_aeb41e3e-f6e0-46da-bc70-bae1f75fbd85" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S17C6</sptc><title id="_20772044-6b2f-474b-bd6d-c1490fceb7c4">Sprinkler valve enclosures</title><archive-num>2019: Spec E1.5: 6</archive-num><subclause id="_703ccace-56b0-41a3-b3e7-47f3b8e5a511" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_090f5c1c-dc4b-42a1-a36d-9d49a10ea3f2">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Sprinkler alarm valves must be located in a secure room or enclosure which has direct egress to a road or open space.</p></subclause><subclause id="_51f8f126-f6fd-4ea2-859f-902a4c687a5e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d0dc8540-fbe1-4639-b34b-07a5a5be1706">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>All sprinkler valve rooms and enclosures must be secured with a system suitable for use by the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1275_0.4.0.xml#_cc69b717-0915-4071-87d9-176353f8cc9a" id="_07b5bea4-3f4a-49a8-974a-64aeec7c61c4" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire brigade</xref>.</p></subclause></clause>